metadata.name: CHAPTER 1 - THE TRACER
metadata.description:
Chapter One: This is the beginning of the meeting and finally become their friendship. BB (a tracer), BigEye (a little monster) and BabyEye (an orphan girl).

The monster hunter duo came to inspect the old gas station after being informed that monsters were rampaging in the area. But it turned out that it was only a girl wearing monster costume. At the end, the two took the girl back with them. 

This work is digital hand sketch and coloring.  
6750 x 9000 px
